code: @Override protected CamelContext createCamelContext() throws Exception {     CamelContext context = super.createCamelContext().     context.init().     // to force a different management name than the camel id     context.getManagementNameStrategy().setNamePattern("20-#name#").     return context. }

@Test public void testManagedCamelContextCreateRouteStaticEndpointJson() throws Exception {     // JMX tests dont work well on AIX CI servers (hangs them)     if (isPlatform("aix")) {         return.     }     MBeanServer mbeanServer = getMBeanServer().     ObjectName on = ObjectName.getInstance("org.apache.camel:context=20-camel-1,type=context,name=\"camel-1\"").     // get the json     String json = (String) mbeanServer.invoke(on, "createRouteStaticEndpointJson", null, null).     assertNotNull(json).     assertEquals(2, StringHelper.countChar(json, '{')).     assertEquals(2, StringHelper.countChar(json, '}')). }
